cu.explanation_en: Setting the ciphering algorithm to an unknown enum 'nea9' will cause negotiation failure during the security setup phase.

du.explanation_en: Setting nb_tx to an out-of-range value will cause radio unit configuration errors and initialization failure.
du.explanation_zh: 將 nb_tx 設定為超出範圍的值將導致無線單元配置錯誤和初始化失敗。
